recommendations.Name: Lemonade Muffins
recommendations.RecipeInstructions: c("Mix dry ingredients in a bowl.", "In another bowl, mix only 1/2 cup lemonade, egg, milk, and oil.", "Add to dry mix, stirring until just moistened.", "Gently stir in nuts.", "Spoon into prepared pans and bake and bake at 375ºF.", "for 15-20 mins or tests clean.", "While hot, brush with remaining lemonade and sprinkle with white sugar.", "Makes 8-9 large muffins.")

recommendations.Name: Zucchini Ribbons With Basil Butter
recommendations.RecipeIngredientParts: c("zucchini", "butter", "olive oil", "parmesan cheese", "fresh basil leaves", "red pepper flakes")
recommendations.RecipeInstructions: c("Bring pot of water to boil.", "Mean-while, with vegetable peeler-slice zucchini lengthwise into ribbons.  Add zucchini to boiling water; cook until tender, 30-60 seconds.", "Drain and transfer zucchini to serving bowl.", "Add butter, oil, parmesan, basil, and red pepper flakes; gently toss until butter is melted and zucchini are coated.", "I also added 1/2 tsp of garlic powder to this!")

recommendations.Name: Roast Beef Horseradish Spirals
recommendations.RecipeIngredientParts: c("cream cheese", "green onions", "fresh parsley", "salt", "garlic powder", "deli roast beef", "10-inch flour tortillas")
recommendations.RecipeInstructions: c("Combine first 6 ingredients.", "Place the two tortillas on work surface, spread half of cheese over each, top each with half of the roast beef slices, leaving a 1/2 inch border around edges.", "Roll up, wrap tightly in plastic wrap.", "Refrigerate until firm, 30 minutes or up to 1 day ahead.", "cut diagonally into 1/2 inch slices and serve.")
